        <li>Oversaw regulation review, led product testing, and supported global product registrations for new products and change management initiatives.</li>
        <li>Led cross-functional teams to resolve compliance-related technical challenges.</li>
        <li>Built and managed the regulatory database as well as its interface with SAP to ensures all safety, regulatory, and quality information is accurately filed, easily accessible, and optimized to support critical business decisions.</li>
        </ul>
